description:
Welcome to my course on "Statistics Concepts-Multiple Regression" This course covers running and evaluating multiple regression models as well as simple linear regression model including assessing the overall quality of models and interpreting individual predictors for significance with PDF Files . We also explore R-Square in depth, including how to interpret R-Square for significance. Together with in-depth coverage of simple regression, we'll also explore correlation, which is closely related to regression analysis. By the end of this course you will be skilled in running and interpreting your own linear regression analyses, as well as critically evaluating the work of others While you can be confident that you are getting accurate information with Quantitative Specialists,

You will Learn

Basic concepts of Multiple Regression like definitions and basic understanding

  • Able to know basic concepts of Multiple Regression
  • What is simple linear regression analysis?
  • What is Multiple Regression? Estimation of Multiple Linear Regression Model with Two Explanatory Variables
  • Introducing the formulas of Multiple Regression in deviation form
  • All Examples of simple linear regression model and Multiple Regression Model step by step with easy methods
  • In this course you can download PDF files which consists of examples and exercises that for additional help .
  • So Enroll Today , Create Change and be Amazing!
title: Multiple Regression Step by Step ( A Complete Course )
